{"tid":1924350,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"專訪袁國勇 — 相信科學，在悲觀中學會樂觀","createTime":"2020-03-13T15:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T15:42:32.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"314e81a0450bb45d9753eefd0d97181f64dda483","tid":1924350,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:41:09.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯勿寄望藥物疫苗 把抗疫成為生活<br />\n<br />\n新藥物「瑞德西韋」已抵港，這款原來用作對抗伊波拉病毒的藥物，在多項測試中都被認為有效對抗武漢肺炎病毒，但袁國勇坦言，以為有藥物便可處理是「不設實際的幻想」，「就算真的有這款藥，當全世界也在搶，你連口罩也搶不到，這些昂貴、稀有的藥物，我們會有嗎？」「疫苗也是，研發成功，都已經兩、三年後，到時可能已經很多人得到抗體了。」<br />\n<br />\n他還是用平淡的聲線去宣布「壞消息」，「不要不設實際，做好保護措施最重要。」<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8-%E5%9C%A8%E6%82%B2%E8%A7%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2587%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2582%25B2%25E8%25A7%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25A7%2580%2F&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=df8add76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2587%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2582%25B2%25E8%25A7%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25A7%2580%2F&h=8244f597\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8-%E5%9C%A8%E6%82%B2%E8%A7%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83%E6%A8%82%E8%A7%80/</a>"},{"pid":"07428f00058e16f23c03e298014efd13893dd26a","tid":1924350,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:42:0